title: #129: Ghost Huntin and the New Age Woooo with Ryan Singer
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another interesting episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode Sam welcomes paranormal expert and ufologist, Ryan Singer, to discuss the spirit realm! Check out Ryan's podcast "Me & Paranormal You" and his new comedy album "Free Love" that's about to drop Oct 12th.
http://ryansingercomedy.com/me-and-paranormal-you/
